Package com.odiago.common.flags

Class Summary
FlagParser Provides a static method init(), used to parse flags from a command line.
 

Exception Summary
DuplicateFlagException When there are multiple flags declared with the same name.
IllegalFlagValueException Thrown when the value assigned on the command line cannot be coerced into the Java field because it is an incompatible type.
UnrecognizedFlagException When there are multiple flags declared with the same name.
UnsupportedFlagTypeException Thrown when the Java type of the flag is not supported.
 

Annotation Types Summary
Flag Annotates fields that should be assigned to when a command-line is parsed.
